title: Kim Kardashian Sends Her First Snapchat Ever
text: Though her sister Kylie Jenner is all over Snapchat all the time, Kim Kardashian hasn't adopted the platform just yet, at least not publicly . On Monday night at Cosmopolitan 's 50th birthday party, Kim sent her first ~official~ Snapchat with the help of Snapchat master Kylie, and of course it was flawless. Perhaps this taste of Snapchat glory will inspire her to start her own account and send messages from inside the private jet!
